      <title>乌干达宪法法院拒绝推翻严厉的反 LGBTQ 法</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/ugandan-court-rejects-bid-to-overturn-draconian-anti-lgbtq-law</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌干达宪法法院驳回了一项要求废除该国严格的反 LGBTQ 立法的请愿书，该立法导致世界银行暂停提供资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/ugandan-court-rejects-bid-to-overturn-draconian-anti-lgbtq-law</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 08:06:45 GMT</pubDate>
