      <title>莫斯科在弹药争夺战中超越乌克兰盟友</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/russia-is-outpacing-ukraine-s-allies-in-the-race-for-ammunition</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰及其盟国在获取基辅抵御俄罗斯袭击所需弹药的竞赛中正在失败。]]></description>
