    <item>
      <title>因政治分裂，以色列人团结起来反抗全球孤立</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/divided-by-politics-israelis-unite-to-defy-global-isolation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当十万名抗议者在外面高喊要求提前选举时，以色列总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡周日举行新闻发布会，为他在加沙战争中的行为辩护。有人问他为什么世界越来越反对以色列。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/divided-by-politics-israelis-unite-to-defy-global-isolation</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 07:04:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>塞内加尔总统任命民粹主义领袖为总理</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/senegal-s-president-appoints-firebrand-leader-as-prime-minister</link>
      <description><![CDATA[塞内加尔新总统任命奥斯曼·桑科为总理，提升了在上个月的选举中支持他竞选的民粹主义反对派领导人的权力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/senegal-s-president-appoints-firebrand-leader-as-prime-minister</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 05:29:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国法院接受解散最高反对党的请愿书</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/thai-court-accepts-petition-to-disband-largest-opposition-party</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国宪法法院已接受解散该国最大反对党的请愿书，该党此前因修改该国严格的王室诽谤法而被判违反宪章。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/thai-court-accepts-petition-to-disband-largest-opposition-party</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 05:06:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普法官因审判计划“有缺陷”而受到检察官的攻击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/trump-judge-assailed-by-prosecutor-over-flawed-trial-planning</link>
      <description><![CDATA[因不当处理机密文件而起诉前总统唐纳德·特朗普的司法部特别检察官向负责此案的法官表达了不满，称她对关键法律问题的理解似乎“存在根本缺陷”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/trump-judge-assailed-by-prosecutor-over-flawed-trial-planning</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 04:40:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>调查显示莫迪联盟将在印度主要邦赢得最多选票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/modi-alliance-to-win-most-votes-in-key-india-state-survey-shows</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据全国选举前两周发布的一项民意调查，印度总理纳伦德拉·莫迪领导的政党预计将在该国人口最多的邦获得多数选票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/modi-alliance-to-win-most-votes-in-key-india-state-survey-shows</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 01:53:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>金正恩领导测试可击中美国基地的新型导弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/kim-jong-un-leads-test-of-new-missile-that-can-hit-us-bases</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据朝鲜官方媒体报道，朝鲜领导人金正恩监督了新型弹道导弹的测试，该导弹旨在部署可运载核弹头的高超音速滑翔飞行器，并称这次测试是“划时代的成功”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/kim-jong-un-leads-test-of-new-missile-that-can-hit-us-bases</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 00:19:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登、习近平通电话谈论人工智能风险、俄罗斯和芬太尼</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/biden-xi-spoke-by-phone-to-manage-world-tensions-opportunities</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统乔·拜登和中国国家主席习近平周二通电话，这是自去年 11 月在加州会晤以来他们的首次一对一沟通。]]></description>
